<div class="about">
  <div class="container pt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="pb-3 mt-5 mb-4 font-weight-bold text-label">About Us</h1>
        <div class="text-muted pr-4">
          We are a Not-for-Profit team that is aiming for quality education across the country. 
          Our platform finds tutors for the community children to study in small localised groups at 
          subsidised fees that have been agreed upon by the teachers and the parents of the grouped children.
          <br><br>
          Ever since the COVID-19 education lockdown, our children have been seated home and 
          are wearing away academically, and with the recently increased school lockdown for lower primary, 
          we believe home schooling is a viable option to keep the children occupied academically.
          <br><br>
          Our job is to create study-groups and add children or students according to their proximity and then 
          match them with a willing and qualified teacher.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 ml-auto pt-5">
        <%= image_tag("about.jpg", :alt => "", class: "img-fluid shadow", style: "border-radius: 1.6em 0 0 0; margin-top: 4em") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="how">
    <div class="container pt-5">
        <h1 class="pb-3 mt-5 mb-5 text-center font-weight-bold text-label">How it works</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="how-to how-to-1">
                  <h1>🧒</h1>
                  <h4>Register Child</h4>
                  <p>As a parent, register your child with us <a href="https://homeschool.ug/children/new" class="text-white border-bottom">here</a></p>
                </div>  
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="how-to how-to-2">
                  <h1>🧑🏽‍🤝‍🧑🏽</h1>
                  <h4>Form a Group</h4>
                  <p>
                    A Study Group is formed by our system when children 
                    in the same area are registered.
                  </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="how-to how-to-3">
                    <h1>👩🏽‍🏫</h1>
                    <h4>Find Teachers</h4>
                    <p>
                      A group is allocated a teacher in the same area to teach and guide it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="how-to how-to-4">
                    <h1>📖</h1>
                    <h4>Happy Learning</h4>
                    <p>
                      We check on the progress of each study group occasionally.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

